      <title>交易者开始定位债券收益率下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-26/traders-start-positioning-for-drop-in-bond-yields-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着交易员押注更大的降低利率，美国财政收益率接近一年的最低水平。一些债券交易者开始对可能的经济放缓进行对冲。彭博的利兹·卡波·麦考密克（Liz Capo McCormick）以“彭博公开兴趣”的身份获得了华尔街的殴打。 （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-26/traders-start-positioning-for-drop-in-bond-yields-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Feb 2025 17:01:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>为什么Hooters考虑破产计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-26/hooters-considers-bankruptcy-plan-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国及其债权人正在考虑一项潜在的破产计划，该计划将对该品牌的控制权归还前高管和连锁店的原始父母。 Eliza Ronalds-Hannon报告了“彭博公开兴趣”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-26/hooters-considers-bankruptcy-plan-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Feb 2025 16:53:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
